  "title": "Desktop Support Engineer",
  "description": "<p>📢 Hiring: Onsite Desktop Support Engineer</p><p>📍 Location: Singapore</p><p>🧑‍💻 Experience: 3–5 Years</p><p>🖥️ Role: Digital Workplace Computing</p><p>Open to: Singapore Citizens & PR only</p><p>Key Responsibilities:</p><p>* Onsite desktop support for Windows (Domain) & macOS</p><p>* OS imaging & installation (Windows 10, macOS)</p><p>* Install & upgrade OS and software</p><p>* Support MS Office applications</p><p>* Resolve user tickets (hardware & software)</p><p>* Build & install PCs, phones & peripherals</p><p>* Asset management & maintenance</p><p>* Multitasking across multiple machines</p><p>* Create technical documentation & manuals</p><p>* Vendor coordination</p><p>* Basic knowledge of Windows, Intune & JAMF</p><p>Must-Have Skills:</p><p>* Strong troubleshooting skills</p><p>* Excellent communication & interpersonal skills</p><p>* Customer-first, solution-oriented mindset</p><p></p><p>📩 Interested candidates, please share your CV to muthumala@lionandelephants.com.</p>",
